{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766254648,"text":"The blog entry card will have a hero image in the left. The title and description beside and the tags on top. There is no draft mode. So remove the draft tag. A neu tag shall be used to name the location of the blog (manually entered later) and the date."}
