{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766254868,"text":"Clicking on one blog entry will open the blog entry detail page. This page shows the entry hereo image on top, the map hovering on the right with a pin on the location of this entry. The header area also contains a showt description of the entry. Below is a full size text element for the journal entry including text and images. Below there ist a photo gallery with all the photos from the text but also more photos."}
{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766255017,"text":"In the detail page place the hero image ab background image on the top side of the page. The map hovers on the right as now. The Text for title and description also hovers on the background photo."}
{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766255098,"text":"On the main page there is a \"Add new entry\" button on the lower left side of the header hero picture."}
{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766255181,"text":"The detail page has an edit mode. This enables the text editor for the title, description as well as text. It also enables a \"+\" button ont he Photos section. Rename \"Photos\" to media."}
