{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766256333,"text":"Core problem: Travellers want to organize the travel reports in a web app. So they can review later or show the travel to somebody elso."}
{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766256411,"text":"1. solo travellers and couples are tpyical. The creator of a travel is one person. But this person may add more friends for either viewing the trip or also contributing."}
{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766256463,"text":"Now the use other web sides. These are sometimes cost-intensive or only provide smartphone apps."}
{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766256489,"text":"C"}
{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766256621,"text":"Primary users want to organize the memories of trips, share them with friends and sometimes organize memories with companions of the trip. Viewers are family or friends not participating the trip but interested in. They look every day if there are new blog entries and read them. So they can virtually be part of the trip."}
{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766256646,"text":"C"}
{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766256741,"text":"The creator will typically add an entry every day of the trip. Between the trips may be weeks or month wihtout entries. Viewers will look at the trip daily but only if there is an active trip. Sharing means invting other users (e.g. by email) to the blog."}
{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766256762,"text":"C"}
{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766256801,"text":"looks good"}
{"session_id":"019b3cd4-2000-7553-b475-7027684d1f18","ts":1766256824,"text":"C"}
